Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nat... Nanami can see Nat and her servants...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nat, Queen of Gold. She claims to be the creator of the Golden Vortex.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Creator my butt. If this piece of shit is behind those experiments, then she is worse than the Corrupted.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami saw it, the laboratory you found, Karenina...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'You, me, every invader... Nat sees us all. When Nanami hacked into her network, I synced with her "vision."', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'How about Roland? Did you see him?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nat could see everyone but Roland... But Nanami also found the Gray Ravens and Commandant taken by Nat! Nanami wants to save Commandant!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "If their commandant has been taken, we'll have to rethink our whole operation... But our comms is not working, and Babylonia doesn't know yet...", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Forget Roland! Saving Gray Raven is our priority! Rescuing Commandant is more important than everything else!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'We have a blueprint now! Nanami, can you find out where Nat is?', 4: '2'}
